{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id4670eddc-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6042"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"6042"},"text":"§ 6042.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Returns regarding payments of dividends and corporate earnings and profits","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id4670eddd-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6042/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Requirement of reporting","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4670edde-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6042/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Every person—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id4670eddf-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6042/a/1/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" who makes payments of dividends aggregating $10 or more to any other person during any calendar year, or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id4670ede0-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6042/a/1/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" who receives payments of dividends as a nominee and who makes payments aggregating $10 or more during any calendar year to any other person with respect to the dividends so received,","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n\n"},{"tag":"continuation","attrib":{},"text":"shall make a return according to the forms or regulations prescribed by the Secretary, setting forth the aggregate amount of such payments and the name and address of the person to whom paid.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4670ede1-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6042/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Returns required by the Secretary","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Every person who makes payments of dividends aggregating less than $10 to any other person during any calendar year shall, when required by the Secretary, make a return setting forth the aggregate amount of such payments, and the name and address of the person to whom paid.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id4670ede2-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6042/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Dividend defined","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4670ede3-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6042/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" General rule","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"For purposes of this section, the term “dividend” means—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id4670ede4-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6042/b/1/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" any distribution by a corporation which is a dividend (as defined in section 316); and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id4670ede5-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6042/b/1/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" any payment made by a stockbroker to any person as a substitute for a dividend (as so defined).","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4670ede6-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6042/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Exceptions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"For purposes of this section, the term “dividend” does not include any distribution or payment—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id4670ede7-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6042/b/2/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" to the extent provided in regulations prescribed by the Secretary—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"id4670ede8-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6042/b/2/A/i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"i"},"text":"(i)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" by a foreign corporation, or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"id4670ede9-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6042/b/2/A/ii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"ii"},"text":"(ii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" to a foreign corporation, a nonresident alien, or a partnership not engaged in a trade or business in the United States and composed in whole or in part of nonresident aliens, or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id4670edea-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6042/b/2/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" except to the extent otherwise provided in regulations prescribed by the Secretary, to any person described in section 6049(b)(4).","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4670edeb-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6042/b/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Special rule","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"If the person making any payment described in subsection (a)(1)(A) or (B) is unable to determine the portion of such payment which is a dividend or is paid with respect to a dividend, he shall, for purposes of subsection (a)(1), treat the entire amount of such payment as a dividend or as an amount paid with respect to a dividend.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id4670edec-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6042/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Statements to be furnished to persons with respect to whom information is required","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Every person required to make a return under subsection (a) shall furnish to each person whose name is required to be set forth in such return a written statement showing—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4670eded-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6042/c/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the name, address, and phone number of the information contact of the person required to make such return, and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4670edee-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6042/c/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the aggregate amount of payments to the person required to be shown on the return.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n\n"},{"tag":"continuation","attrib":{},"text":"The written statement required under the preceding sentence shall be furnished (either in person or in a statement mailing by first-class mail which includes adequate notice that the statement is enclosed) to the person on or before January 31 of the year following the calendar year for which the return under subsection (a) was required to be made and shall be in such form as the Secretary may prescribe by regulations.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id4670edef-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6042/d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"d"},"text":"(d)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Statements to be furnished by corporations to Secretary","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Every corporation shall, when required by the Secretary—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4670edf0-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6042/d/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" furnish to the Secretary a statement stating the name and address of each shareholder, and the number of shares owned by each shareholder;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4670edf1-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6042/d/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" furnish to the Secretary a statement of such facts as will enable him to determine the portion of the earnings and profits of the corporation (including gains, profits, and income not taxed) accumulated during such periods as the Secretary may specify, which have been distributed or ordered to be distributed, respectively, to its shareholders during such taxable years as the Secretary may specify; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4670edf2-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s6042/d/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" furnish to the Secretary a statement of its accumulated earnings and profits and the names and addresses of the individuals or shareholders who would be entitled to such accumulated earnings and profits if divided or distributed, and of the amounts that would be payable to each.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id4670edf3-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1954-08-16/ch736"},"text":"Aug. 16, 1954, ch. 736","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/68A/746"},"text":"68A Stat. 746","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/87/834/s19/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 87–834, § 19(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1962-10-16"},"text":"Oct. 16, 1962","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/76/1053"},"text":"76 Stat. 1053","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/455/tXIX/s1906/b/13/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–455, title XIX, § 1906(b)(13)(A)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1976-10-04"},"text":"Oct. 4, 1976","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/90/1834"},"text":"90 Stat. 1834","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/248/tIII"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–248, title III","children":[],"tail":", §§ 303(a), 308(a), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1982-09-03"},"text":"Sept. 3, 1982","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/96/587"},"text":"96 Stat. 587","children":[],"tail":", 591; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/354/s5/a/40"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–354, § 5(a)(40)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1982-10-19"},"text":"Oct. 19, 1982","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/96/1696"},"text":"96 Stat. 1696","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/98/67/tI"},"text":"Pub. L. 98–67, title I","children":[],"tail":", §§ 102(a), 108(b), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1983-08-05"},"text":"Aug. 5, 1983","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/97/369"},"text":"97 Stat. 369","children":[],"tail":", 383; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/98/369/dA/tVII/s714/d"},"text":"Pub. L. 98–369, div. A, title VII, § 714(d)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1984-07-18"},"text":"July 18, 1984","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/98/961"},"text":"98 Stat. 961","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/514/tXV/s1501/c/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–514, title XV, § 1501(c)(2)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1986-10-22"},"text":"Oct. 22, 1986","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/100/2736"},"text":"100 Stat. 2736","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/168/tXII/s1201/a/3"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–168, title XII, § 1201(a)(3)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1996-07-30"},"text":"July 30, 1996","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/110/1469"},"text":"110 Stat. 1469","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id4670edf4-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id4670edf5-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id4670edf6-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1996—Subsec. (c)(1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/168"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–168","children":[],"tail":" substituted “name, address, and phone number of the information contact” for “name and address”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1986—Subsec. (c). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/514"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–514","children":[],"tail":", in amending subsec. (c) generally, substituted “information is required” for “information is furnished” in heading and, in text, substituted references to persons required to make returns for former references to persons making returns and struck out provisions directing that no statement was required to be furnished to any person under this subsection if the aggregate amount of payments to such person as shown on the return made under subsec. (a)(1) was less than $10."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1984—Subsec. (b)(2). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/98/369"},"text":"Pub. L. 98–369","children":[],"tail":", in amending par. (2) generally, designated existing provision as subpar. (A), redesignated as cls. (i) and (ii) of subpar. (A) text formerly designated (A) and (B), and added subpar. (B)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1983—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/98/67"},"text":"Pub. L. 98–67","children":[],"tail":" substituted in subsec. (c) “The written statement required under the preceding sentence shall be furnished (either in person or in a separate mailing by first-class mail) to the person on or before January 31 of the year following the calendar year for which the return under subsection (a) was made, and shall be in such form as the Secretary may prescribe by regulations” for “The written statement required under the preceding sentence shall be furnished to the person on or before January 31 of the year following the calendar year for which the return under subsection (a)(1) was made” and repealed amendments made by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/248"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–248","children":[],"tail":". See 1982 Amendment note below."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1982—Subsecs. (a)(1), (c), (e). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/248"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–248","children":[],"tail":" provided that, applicable to payments of interest, dividends, and patronage dividends paid or credited after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1983-06-30"},"text":"June 30, 1983","children":[],"tail":", subsecs. (a)(1) and (c) are amended and a new subsec. (e) is added. Section 102(a), (b) of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/98/67/tI"},"text":"Pub. L. 98–67, title I","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1983-08-05"},"text":"Aug. 5, 1983","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/97/369"},"text":"97 Stat. 369","children":[],"tail":", repealed subtitle A (§§ 301–308) of title III of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/248"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–248","children":[],"tail":" as of the close of "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1983-06-30"},"text":"June 30, 1983","children":[],"tail":", and provided that the Internal Revenue Code of 1954 [now 1986] [this title] shall be applied and administered (subject to certain exceptions) as if such subtitle A (and the amendments made by such subtitle A) had not been enacted."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b)(2). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/354"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–354","children":[],"tail":" redesignated cl. (A)(i) as subpar. (A) and cl. (A)(ii) as subpar. (B). Former subpar. (B), excluding from the term “dividends” any amount described in section 1373 (relating to undistributed taxable income of electing small business corporations), was struck out."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1976—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/455"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–455","children":[],"tail":" struck out “or his delegate” after “Secretary” wherever appearing."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1962—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/87/834"},"text":"Pub. L. 87–834","children":[],"tail":" substituted “Returns regarding payments of dividends and corporate earnings and profits” for “Returns regarding corporate dividends, earnings, and profits” in section catchline, added subsecs. (a) to (c), designated existing provisions of section as subsec. (d), and substituted in par. (1) of subsec. (d) “furnish to the Secretary or his delegate a statement stating the name and address of each shareholder, and the number of shares owned by each shareholder” for “Make a return of its payments of dividends, stating the name and address of, the number of shares owned by, and the amount of dividends paid to, each shareholder.”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"id4670edf7-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text"